  "text": "While the term cosegmentation has been coined by [CITATION_1] , our approach significantly differs from their approach, which is based on comparing histograms. On the contrary, our approach is morphological in the sense that it attempts to identify overlapping regions in two images by finding an optimal tree assignment.",
